-------------------------------------------------------------------------
List of files/file
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
task2.c:C file demonstrating event handling for various cases (thread running,thread running realtime,thread blocked by semaphore and thread is delayed).

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Steps to run the code
----------------------------------------------------------------------
1.Compile the code and generate object file using make file make command.
2.Execute the program with command "sudo ./task2.o"
3.To perform ftrace run using command "sudo trace-cmd record -e sched_switch -e signal taskset 0x01 ./task2.o"
3.After the program finihes executing run kernelshark to check the signal generation and signal delivery.
5.Seperate report file listing all the signal handling has be uploaded with the source code.

